Ms. Groves, kau sepertinya...

498
00:23:30,347 --> 00:23:31,980
Kenapa kau di sini?

499
00:23:31,982 --> 00:23:33,914
Hanya memastikan kalau kita benar tentang...

500
00:23:33,916 --> 00:23:37,118
